Tanker: please write when you are sober or ?, you repeated entire paragraphs..by the way, I refused my student deferment and was classified 1-A, even took my physical twice and passed it.  By the the way, while I was avoiding VIET NAM, I took a year to wander around Europe, ended up in Israel, 1967, and went though the 6 day war there. So perhaps I am not the total cherry you want me to be. I stood in a trench with an UZI in my hands, sorry it was not an M 16, but the Jews make a better weapon (not anti-sematic by the way, thay are my people), I even have a picture of me and Moshe Dayan together to prove my point.  The reality is that you should have never been in Nam. PERIOD.They never asked you to come, only the american puppet government asked you in.<br><br>
Jeffrey Winkler-Hurray, Another thinking man joins the fray.<br><br>
Tanker, stop trying to justify our past involvement. I and no one I knew fault you for being had, I never called your wife and I spit upon any one who whould do such a thing, but like Hernandez who writes here, and would have us all think that every soldier ran a gaunlet of spitters and baby killer screaming civilians, it just wasn't so.  At the very end of the war, the not so silent majority finally got there head out of their ballot, and voiced their contempt, but not before that. American's hate losers. Could it be, and wrongfully so, that you get sweep up into that corporate-nationalistic logic? And are seen as losers, instead of as victims????<br>
Once more, let me say, I took no deferment, I did my 2 years, I got no G.I.Bill, I faught in a war too (in another country that did it in 6 days), and I book no evil, no bull shit (my favorite phrase) and if we ever meet, I'll be the first to buy...   by the way,.. I became a shrink because of being a hippy doper first, not a war protestor, seemed I had a natural ability to talk bummer trips down, and help define reality, something I seem to be doing again alot of the time these days on the web. Soon I will have my own site and you can come and throw cyber stones at it.<br>
